            "text_dY6wmH": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>An Olfactory Art Studio - Our purpose is to illustrate the power of scent beyond the limitations of a perfume bottle. </p><p>Viti Vinci is an olfactory art studio creating scent art through installations, commissions, and collectible wearable editions, rooted in regenerative matter and archetypal storytelling, whilst confronting global challenges with beauty, hope, and impact. <br/><br/>The studio exists to translate the tensions of our time into olfactory artworks, connecting us with the world around us in the most direct, pre-linguistic manner. <br/><br/>The studio strives to reconnect to the land, to its soil, to our community, to our memories, to our emotions and to our values.</p>",
                "width": "100%",
                "max_width": "none",
                "alignment": "left",
                "type_preset": "rte",
                "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
