            "text_6BTWa9": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Olfactory artworks, limited edition art perfumes, private commissions.</p><p>Olfactory Artwork is a work where scent is the primary medium, whether it be for an installation, an object, or a private commission.<br/><br/>Perfume art collections are curated bodies of wearable works, released as collectible editions, inspired by art and archetypes. Conceptually rigorous, limited in number, designed to be collected.<br/><br/>The studio of Creative Director, Victor Alarcon is fluid, working all over the world, with multiple partners and artists, but will always be anchored by the botanical farm, and perfume lab in Palma, Mallorca.</p>",
